Sentencas: NiO-Al2O3 nanocomposite has been synthesized by mixing combustion synthesized powders.
Titulo: Characterization of NiO-Al2O3 composite and its conductivity in biogas for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The nanocomposite is an effective anode/anode functional layer for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Characterization of NiO-Al2O3 composite and its conductivity in biogas for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The TEM of NiO and Al2O3 revealed spherical particles of 30 nm and platelets of 70 nm, respectively.
Titulo: Characterization of NiO-Al2O3 composite and its conductivity in biogas for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The XRD analysis of NiO-Al2O3 composite sintered at 900 degrees C showed presence of cubic NiO and rhombohedral alpha-Al2O3 which were chemically stable.
Titulo: Characterization of NiO-Al2O3 composite and its conductivity in biogas for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: However, above 1200 degrees C NiAl2O4 started to appear.
Titulo: Characterization of NiO-Al2O3 composite and its conductivity in biogas for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The conductivity of NiO-Al2O3 was the highest in hydrogen (4.3 x 10(-3) S/cm at 600 degrees C).
Titulo: Characterization of NiO-Al2O3 composite and its conductivity in biogas for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In biogas, the conductivity was 3.2 x 10(-3) S/cm with the activation energy of 0.67 eV.
